{"tid":1101864,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"動物朋友2  未成年飲酒疑惑 聲優 監督 接待","createTime":"2019-04-11T10:08:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-11T15:29:43.000Z","uid":150609,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"cbba5d39fb423a8e8a6c1ab1866f97891fb1ea40","tid":1101864,"uid":150609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T10:08:01.000Z","msg":"動物朋友2 最終回12話在2018年4/2 深夜2時放送<br />\n 一眾staff在居酒屋一同觀看 慶功宴 <br />\n<br />\n被發現同席有未成年女聲優參與 深夜飲酒會<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yNytcg4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyNytcg4.jpg&h=a2a1f14b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n菅まどか<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hHEW5CM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhHEW5CM.jpg&h=2faccec4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日前角川將舉辦的《動物朋友 2》徵選聲優選考會聲明中，也引發了不小的波紋。<br />\n首先是關於聲優徵選的條件，選考會聲明表示歡迎 16 到 20 歲，沒有經驗且沒有經紀公司的女性參加，提交履歷時還必須附上三圍資料。光在這個部份就引起粉絲們的爭議，質疑為何徵選聲優需要求三圍資料。"},{"pid":"efb9b9794c47b9e3db1c953464a2af821e23a184","tid":1101864,"uid":247554,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T10:49:29.000Z","msg":"得一個女？"},{"pid":"0d3ed151e1d7ef2d3d0cca88ce187eda1dcd3c74","tid":1101864,"uid":56277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T10:51:57.000Z","msg":"細谷 木村 兩個毒瘤 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ae5a1e1d85bf8448babd450d7a18d633b531bab","tid":1101864,"uid":173852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T10:53:19.000Z","msg":"慶功？慶乜功？"},{"pid":"f8b4fa16b3ea23851c680ca3bd66b77b9ddf9e92","tid":1101864,"uid":183026,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T10:54:21.000Z","msg":"重有面慶功？定慶祝搞爛一套野？"},{"pid":"6b0519439a1f03a8f77514d90163a0dd53db7ee0","tid":1101864,"uid":123848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T10:56:34.000Z","msg":"未成年都入得居酒屋，所以？"},{"pid":"df6d561d1a5d93a67cc29ba429a7bd788f3d